            "tag": "p",
            "html": "Given below are all the possible fields that are allowed for a transaction. As seen in the above image, The account field is not necessarily present in the field provided to add the transaction. <a href=\"https://help.blitzbudget.com/en/transactions/how-to-select-a-financial-account/\" class=\"article-anchor\"> Select an account for adding a transaction </a>."
		},
        {
            "tag": "div",
            "classInfo": "item-container",
            "html": "<div class=\"icon\">1</div><div class=\"copy-container\"><p class=\"description mb-3\">Account <i class=\"small tripleNineColor\">(required)</i></p></div>"
		},
        {
            "tag": "div",
            "classInfo": "item-container",
            "html": "<div class=\"icon\">2</div><div class=\"copy-container\"><p class=\"description mb-3\">Category <i class=\"small tripleNineColor\">(required)</i></p></div>"
