        {
            "tag": "h3",
            "html": "Schedule Transaction"
		},
        {
            "tag": "p",
            "html": "Scheduling a transaction is as simple as choosing between these recurrence option's <strong>WEEKLY</strong>, <strong>BI-MONTHLY</strong>, <strong>MONTHLY</strong> while adding a transaction. Don't worry, <a href=\"https://help.blitzbudget.com/en/transactions/change-recurrence-in-a-scheduled-transaction/\" class=\"article-anchor\">you can change it when ever you want</a> if you do not want it to recur the next month by editing the transaction later."
		}
